From 3b55a752fbf1218b9267bc09ad0ede22e9d74a5f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: lavenly <135024283+lavenly@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sun, 28 Jun 2026 05:37:36 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] renderengine: remove EGL requirement for legacy GPUs

In Android 10+, SurfaceFlinger's RenderEngine enforces a strict requirement
where the device's EGL driver must advertise support for the
`EGL_RECORDABLE_ANDROID` extension (used for Wi-Fi display mirroring).

Legacy devices, such as those using the Exynos 3475 with an older
Android 5.1/7.1 Mali-T720 GPU driver, physically do not support or expose
this extension. When SurfaceFlinger queries the EGL config with this flag,
it fails to find any matching configurations, triggering a fatal abort:
"no suitable EGLConfig found, giving up". This results in a continuous
bootloop at the LineageOS logo before the system UI can load.

This patch removes the `EGL_RECORDABLE_ANDROID` attribute from the EGL
configuration query in both `GLESRenderEngine` and `SkiaGLRenderEngine`.
By dropping this hard requirement, legacy GPUs are allowed to successfully
select a fallback configuration, properly initializing SurfaceFlinger and
allowing the device to boot into the Android UI.

Generated with Antigravity (https://antigravity.google) using Gemini 3.1 Pro (High)

Change-Id: I73c2dc3252bdacf5162f7a551aeb05e1400dbcab
Signed-off-by: lavenly <135024283+lavenly@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 libs/renderengine/gl/GLESRenderEngine.cpp     | 2 --
 libs/renderengine/skia/SkiaGLRenderEngine.cpp | 2 --
 2 files changed, 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/libs/renderengine/gl/GLESRenderEngine.cpp b/libs/renderengine/gl/GLESRenderEngine.cpp
index 467f848..5156b2f 100644
--- a/libs/renderengine/gl/GLESRenderEngine.cpp
+++ b/libs/renderengine/gl/GLESRenderEngine.cpp
@@ -185,8 +185,6 @@ static status_t selectEGLConfig(EGLDisplay display, EGLint format, EGLint render
         const EGLint tmpAttribs[] = {
                 EGL_RENDERABLE_TYPE,
                 renderableType,
-                EGL_RECORDABLE_ANDROID,
-                EGL_TRUE,
                 EGL_SURFACE_TYPE,
                 EGL_WINDOW_BIT | EGL_PBUFFER_BIT,
                 EGL_FRAMEBUFFER_TARGET_ANDROID,
diff --git a/libs/renderengine/skia/SkiaGLRenderEngine.cpp b/libs/renderengine/skia/SkiaGLRenderEngine.cpp
index e42b5b9..c533630 100644
--- a/libs/renderengine/skia/SkiaGLRenderEngine.cpp
+++ b/libs/renderengine/skia/SkiaGLRenderEngine.cpp
@@ -119,8 +119,6 @@ static status_t selectEGLConfig(EGLDisplay display, EGLint format, EGLint render
         const EGLint tmpAttribs[] = {
                 EGL_RENDERABLE_TYPE,
                 renderableType,
-                EGL_RECORDABLE_ANDROID,
-                EGL_TRUE,
                 EGL_SURFACE_TYPE,
                 EGL_WINDOW_BIT | EGL_PBUFFER_BIT,
                 EGL_FRAMEBUFFER_TARGET_ANDROID,
